Kita lupakan masa lalu,

192
00:11:05,559 --> 00:11:06,400
ulangi dari awal.

193
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:08,320
Aku pasti akan baik padamu, oke?

194
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,559
