195
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:16,280
Tidak terlambat.
Sama sekali tidak terlambat.

196
00:11:17,919 --> 00:11:18,919
Kita pergi ke luar negeri.

197
00:11:19,039 --> 00:11:20,280
Bali, Chiang Mai, Dubai.

198
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:21,799
