pesimis dan putus asa.

227
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:13,880
Jadi, biasanya harus ditemani keluarga.

228
00:13:14,599 --> 00:13:16,640
Keseharian perlu diawasi.

229
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,359
Jika tidak...

230
00:13:20,640 --> 00:13:22,280
Jika tidak, akan bagaimana?

231
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:24,679
Tentu saja,

232
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:26,559
yang kubilang itu pasien depresi parah.

233
00:13:27,640 --> 00:13:28,799
