Baik. Terima kasih Dokter.

715
00:36:18,159 --> 00:36:19,239
Baik, sama-sama.

716
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:38,919
Fanlu.

717
00:36:39,879 --> 00:36:41,399
Jika benar-benar terjadi sesuatu padamu,

718
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:44,040
