719
00:36:45,439 --> 00:36:49,120
Jika aku mati, semuanya bisa tenang.

720
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:50,760
Bukankah begitu?

721
00:36:52,040 --> 00:36:53,479
Kenapa kau berkata seperti itu?

722
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:55,199
Fanlu.

723
